Joe Flynn (American actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joe_Flynn_(American_actor) 0 Joseph A. Flynn (November 8, 1924 – July 19, 1974) was an American character actor. He was best known for his role in the 1960s ABC television situation comedy McHale's Navy. He was also a frequent guest star on 1960s TV shows, such as Batman, and appeared in several Walt Disney film comedies.
